content:
The OmniStudio content and runtime, standard OmniStudio content, and Omnistudio basics are described. 

OmniScripts, FlexCards, data mappers, integration procedures, and various actions within them such as assert action, batch action, Chatter action, decision matrix action, delete action, DocuSign envelope action, email action, expression set action, HTTP action, list action, remote action, response action are explained. 

Integration procedure best practices, cache, error handling, environment variables, external objects, test procedures, and security for data mappers and integration procedures are covered.

The Chatter Action creates a Chatter post and sends it to a Chatter feed.
title: Omnistudio Data Mappers and Integration Procedures
